TITLE: Configuring Fastify to Listen on All IPv4 Interfaces
DESCRIPTION: Example of how to modify the Fastify server to listen on all available IPv4 interfaces instead of just localhost. This is useful for deploying in containerized environments.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastify/fastify/blob/main/docs/Guides/Getting-Started.md#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
fastify.listen({ port: 3000, host: '0.0.0.0' }, function (err, address) {
  if (err) {
    fastify.log.error(err)
    process.exit(1)
  }
  fastify.log.info(`server listening on ${address}`)
})
```

