TITLE: Parse Request Payloads with Fastify in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript example shows how Fastify parses 'application/json' and 'text/plain' payloads natively, providing the parsed body through `request.body`. The code snippet sets up a POST route that returns the parsed request body back to the client.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastify/fastify/blob/main/docs/Guides/Getting-Started.md#2025-04-22_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
/**
 * @type {import('fastify').RouteShorthandOptions}
 */
const opts = {}
fastify.post('/', opts, async (request, reply) => {
  return request.body
})
```

