TITLE: Basic Fastify Plugin Structure
DESCRIPTION: The standard structure for a Fastify plugin function with the required parameters: fastify instance, options object, and done callback which must be called when the plugin is ready.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastify/fastify/blob/main/docs/Guides/Plugins-Guide.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
module.exports = function (fastify, options, done) {}
```

