TITLE: Implementing Request Validation
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to validate incoming requests using JSON Schema in Fastify routes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastify/fastify/blob/main/docs/Guides/Getting-Started.md#2025-04-22_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
/**
 * @type {import('fastify').RouteShorthandOptions}
 * @const
 */
const opts = {
  schema: {
    body: {
      type: 'object',
      properties: {
        someKey: { type: 'string' },
        someOtherKey: { type: 'number' }
      }
    }
  }
}

fastify.post('/', opts, async (request, reply) => {
  return { hello: 'world' }
})
```

