TITLE: Starting Fastify Server for Docker Containers
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to start a Fastify server listening on all interfaces (0.0.0.0), which is recommended for Docker container deployments.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastify/fastify/blob/main/docs/Reference/Server.md#2025-04-22_snippet_23

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
fastify.listen({ port: 3000, host: '0.0.0.0' }, (err, address) => {
  if (err) {
    fastify.log.error(err)
    process.exit(1)
  }
})
