TITLE: Stream Piping with Content Type Parsers in Fastify
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to implement stream piping by creating a pass-through content type parser. This allows direct access to the raw request stream for handling file uploads or other streaming operations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastify/fastify/blob/main/docs/Reference/ContentTypeParser.md#2025-04-22_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
fastify.addContentTypeParser('*', function (request, payload, done) {
  done()
})
```

