TITLE: Serialize JSON Responses with Fastify in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code snippet demonstrates how to define a route in Fastify with a response schema that optimizes JSON serialization. The schema defines the structure of the expected response, allowing Fastify to serialize only the specified data. This enhances performance and prevents accidental data leak.
