TITLE: Visualizing Fastify Internal Lifecycle with ASCII Art
DESCRIPTION: This ASCII art diagram illustrates the internal lifecycle of Fastify, showing the flow from incoming request to outgoing response. It includes various hooks, error handling, and the main processing stages.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fastify/fastify/blob/main/docs/Reference/Lifecycle.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: ascii-art
CODE:
```
Incoming Request

   Routing

         Instance Logger

   4**/5** 닳 onRequest Hook

        4**/5** 닳 preParsing Hook

              4**/5** 닳 Parsing

                   4**/5** 닳 preValidation Hook

                            400 닳 Validation

                              4**/5** 닳 preHandler Hook

                                    4**/5** 닳 User Handler

                                                     Reply

